{
  "id": "RAW_03e983f8",
  "title": "信息处理能力，正在悄悄拉开产品经理的差距",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5OTEwNjI2MA==&mid=2651923137&idx=4&sn=e12373cfef493b2c2497f9939cc4523b",
  "date": "2026-01-01 02:02:00",
  "author": "人人都是产品经理",
  "siteName": "人人都是产品经理",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <div data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88287\" data-color=\"#00b0f0\" data-width=\"95%\" style=\"width: 95%;flex: 0 0 95%;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;box-sizing:border-box;max-width:95% !important;\">\n    <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;\">\n     <div style=\"padding:10px;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin-top: 0px;display: block;margin-left: 10px;margin-right: 10px;\"><span style=\"caret-color: red;color: #7f7f7f;font-size: 14px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">面对微信或企业微信里一长段混乱的信息，你是否感到无从下手？本文揭示了信息处理的真正瓶颈——不是理解能力，而是结构化思维。</span></span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"text-align:center;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><strong style=\"caret-color: red;letter-spacing: 0.578px;max-width: 100%;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0px;caret-color: red;font-size: 15px;color: #00b0f0;\"><span leaf=\"\">———— / BEGIN / ————</span></span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">有个画面你肯定熟：</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: red;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">微信一震，</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: red;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">对方甩来一大段话，</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: red;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">不是两三行，是那种——</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: red;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">滑一下还没到底的。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">你盯着屏幕，脑子里有点空；</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: red;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">好像都看懂了，又好像啥也没抓住；</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: red;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">更要命的是，你不知道该怎么回。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">说实话，我以前也这样，</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: red;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">而且越是做产品，越频繁。</span></span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"text-align: justify;margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;display: block;margin-left:10px;margin-right:10px;font-size:17px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 240);font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 240);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我第一次意识到「不是我不行，是文本太乱」</span></span></strong></span></h2>\n   <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">上周还真碰到一次。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">对方在企业微信里，发了快 800 字。</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: red;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">背景、过程、情绪、判断，全揉在一起，</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: red;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">还顺带丢了一句：“这个事情你看怎么推进？”，</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: red;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">我当时的第一反应不是思考，是</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: red;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">烦</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: red;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">真的，烦。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">后来我停了一下，没急着回，而是干了一件以前不会干的事：</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我没读，我先“拆”。</span></span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"text-align: justify;margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;display: block;margin-left:10px;margin-right:10px;font-size:17px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 240);font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 240);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">很多人以为问题是“看不懂”，其实不是</span></span></strong></span></h2>\n   <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们常把问题说成：</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: red;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">“他这段话到底什么意思？”</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">但你冷静一点想，你真的不懂字面意思吗？</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">其实你卡住的点往往是：</span></span></p>\n   <div>\n    <p data-role=\"list\"></p>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: square;margin:0px;padding:0 0 0 30px;list-style-position:outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;color: rgb(127, 127, 127);font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">哪些是事实？</span></span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;color: rgb(127, 127, 127);font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">哪些只是他的判断？</span></span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;color: rgb(127, 127, 127);font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">他为什么要说这么多？</span></span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;color: rgb(127, 127, 127);font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我到底要不要动？</span></span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <p></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">说白了一句话：</span></span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: red;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">你缺的不是阅读理解，是决策前的信息整理。</span></span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这事儿跟语文水平没啥关系。</span></span></p>\n    <h2 style=\"text-align: justify;margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;display: block;margin-left:10px;margin-right:10px;font-size:17px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 240);font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 240);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">打个比方：原始文本就像一锅没滤的汤</span></span></strong></span></h2>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">打个比方：</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">原始长文本，就像一锅刚煮完、还在翻滚的汤：</span></span></p>\n    <div>\n     <p data-role=\"list\"></p>\n     <ul style=\"list-style-type: square;margin:0px;padding:0 0 0 30px;list-style-position:outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n      <li>\n       <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;color: rgb(127, 127, 127);font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">有肉</span></span></p>\n      </li>\n      <li>\n       <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;color: rgb(127, 127, 127);font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">有骨头</span></span></p>\n      </li>\n      <li>\n       <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;color: rgb(127, 127, 127);font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">有油</span></span></p>\n      </li>\n      <li>\n       <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;color: rgb(127, 127, 127);font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">还有浮沫</span></span></p>\n      </li>\n     </ul>\n     <p></p>\n     <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">你要是直接端起来喝，不噎着才怪。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">结构化在干嘛？</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: red;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">就是帮你把汤过一遍筛子，</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: red;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">留下能喝的，把杂质先捞出来。</span></span></p>\n     <h2 style=\"text-align: justify;margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;display: block;margin-left:10px;margin-right:10px;font-size:17px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 240);font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 240);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">高手和普通人的差别，其实就在这一步</span></span></strong></span></h2>\n     <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我观察过一个很明显的分水岭。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"text-align:center;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3476454293628809\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"722\" style=\"vertical-align:baseline;\" data-imgfileid=\"504439466\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f98c8f89&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FicHOSb47jqpUMh0hmssQeTCqfjXnVeItr66JH8DCmzyqpjSljJANeupLqIbr7VaX4xuZGCBYFnE0iaedEcMdCQHA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n     <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">注意啊，这里不是智商差距，</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: red;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">是</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: red;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">处理信息的姿势不一样</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: red;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n     <h2 style=\"text-align: justify;margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;display: block;margin-left:10px;margin-right:10px;font-size:17px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 240);font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 240);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我后来固定用的一套“拆文本”Prompt</span></span></strong></span></h2>\n     <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">后来我干脆不折磨自己了，直接把这件事交给 AI；</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: red;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">但不是“帮我总结”，而是</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: red;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">强制它帮我理结构</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: red;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">下面这套 Prompt，我现在用得非常顺手：</span></span></p>\n     <p data-mpa-preserve-tpl-color=\"t\" data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-preserve=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjttojs4p4i\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></p>\n     <pre style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 16px;\"><code style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:5.95px;white-space:nowrap;display:block;font-size:0.85em;overflow-x:auto;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">你是一名擅长“信息拆解与结构化”的助手。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">我将提供一段【对方发来的原始文本】，请你帮我完成以下任务：</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">1️⃣ 用一句话概括对方整体想表达什么</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">2️⃣ 把内容拆成 3–5 个要点（按逻辑，不按原文顺序）</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">3️⃣ 区分：</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">– 客观事实</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">– 主观判断 / 立场</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">– 情绪或暗示</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">4️⃣ 标出真正需要我回应或决策的点</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">5️⃣ 用大白话解释，不要复述原文要求口语化表达。</span></code></pre>\n     <p></p>\n     <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">第一次用的时候，我真有点惊艳。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">那种感觉，像是把一团毛线一下子拉直了。</span></span></p>\n     <h2 style=\"text-align: justify;margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;display: block;margin-left:10px;margin-right:10px;font-size:17px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;color: rgb(0, 176, 240);font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">话说回来，它到底帮我省了什么？</span></strong></span></h2>\n     <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">不是省时间那么简单。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">它实际帮我干了三件很关键的事：</span></span></p>\n     <p data-role=\"list\"></p>\n     <ol style=\"list-style-type: decimal;margin:0px;padding:0 0 0 30px;list-style-position:outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n      <li>\n       <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;color: rgb(127, 127, 127);font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">把情绪从信息里剥离出来</span></span></p>\n      </li>\n      <li>\n       <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;color: rgb(127, 127, 127);font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">让我知道哪些是“可忽略噪音”</span></span></p>\n      </li>\n      <li>\n       <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;color: rgb(127, 127, 127);font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">明确：我只需要回应哪 1～2 件事</span></span></p>\n      </li>\n     </ol>\n     <p></p>\n     <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">尤其第三点，太重要了。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">很多“沟通内耗”，本质是你在回应对方不需要你回应的部分。</span></span></p>\n     <h2 style=\"text-align: justify;margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;display: block;margin-left:10px;margin-right:10px;font-size:17px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 240);font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 240);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个很容易踩的坑，我得提前说清楚</span></span></strong></span></h2>\n     <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这里得泼一盆冷水：</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: red;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 不是替你下判断。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">它做的是：拆结构、标重点、揪情绪，</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: red;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">但</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: red;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">立场、判断、决策，必须你来。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">别把“像结论”当成“是结论”，</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: red;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">这就像原型评审，工具再好，也只是辅助。</span></span></p>\n     <h2 style=\"text-align: justify;margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;display: block;margin-left:10px;margin-right:10px;font-size:17px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 240);font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 240);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">简单来说：这是信息爆炸时代的底层能力</span></span></strong></span></h2>\n     <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">很多人还在卷：</span></span></p>\n     <div>\n      <p data-role=\"list\"></p>\n      <ul style=\"list-style-type: square;margin:0px;padding:0 0 0 30px;list-style-position:outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n       <li>\n        <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;color: rgb(127, 127, 127);font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">表达能力</span></span></p>\n       </li>\n       <li>\n        <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;color: rgb(127, 127, 127);font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">话术</span></span></p>\n       </li>\n       <li>\n        <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;color: rgb(127, 127, 127);font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">沟通技巧</span></span></p>\n       </li>\n      </ul>\n      <p></p>\n      <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">但我越来越觉得，真正拉开差距的是这一点：</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: red;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">谁能先把混乱信息变成结构，谁就先赢一半。</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">当别人被一大段话拖进细节、情绪、来回纠结时，你已经用几十秒看清了：</span></span></p>\n      <div>\n       <p data-role=\"list\"></p>\n       <ul style=\"list-style-type: square;margin:0px;padding:0 0 0 30px;list-style-position:outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n        <li>\n         <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;color: rgb(127, 127, 127);font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">他在干嘛</span></span></p>\n        </li>\n        <li>\n         <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;color: rgb(127, 127, 127);font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">他想要什么</span></span></p>\n        </li>\n        <li>\n         <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;color: rgb(127, 127, 127);font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我该不该动</span></span></p>\n        </li>\n       </ul>\n       <p></p>\n       <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这不是技巧，这是认知效率。</span></span></p>\n       <h2 style=\"text-align: justify;margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;display: block;margin-left:10px;margin-right:10px;font-size:17px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 240);font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 240);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">你可以立刻做的三件小事</span></span></strong></span></h2>\n       <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">不搞虚的，给你三个马上能用的：</span></span></p>\n       <p data-role=\"list\"></p>\n       <ol style=\"list-style-type: decimal;margin:0px;padding:0 0 0 30px;list-style-position:outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n        <li>\n         <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;color: rgb(127, 127, 127);font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">任何长消息，先不回，先拆</span></span></p>\n        </li>\n        <li>\n         <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;color: rgb(127, 127, 127);font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">回之前问自己一句：「我到底要回应哪一层？」</span></span></p>\n        </li>\n        <li>\n         <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;color: rgb(127, 127, 127);font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">给自己定个规则：「没结构，不决策」</span></span></p>\n        </li>\n       </ol>\n       <p></p>\n       <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">坚持一阵子，你会明显感觉到：消息还是那些消息，但你不再被牵着走了。</span></span></p>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>\n           <div>\n            <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\" data-pm-slice=\"5 6 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;ignored&quot;,&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">\n             <p style=\"text-align:center;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 20px 10px;outline: 0px;clear: both;min-height: 1em;\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0px;caret-color: red;font-size: 15px;color: #00b0f0;\"><span leaf=\"\">———— / E N D / ————</span></span></strong></p>\n             <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:10px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.578px;clear:both;font-size:17px;margin-top:10px;min-height:1em;text-align:justify;margin-right:10px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: #7f7f7f;font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文来自</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">作者：尤里卡高</span></span></span></p>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文提出信息爆炸时代产品经理的核心能力在于信息整理和结构化思维，通过 AI 辅助拆解混乱文本以提升决策效率，避免沟通内耗。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文提出信息爆炸时代产品经理的核心能力在于信息整理和结构化思维，通过 AI 辅助拆解混乱文本以提升决策效率，避免沟通内耗。",
  "summary": "文章深入探讨了在信息爆炸时代，信息处理能力如何悄然拉开了产品经理之间的差距。作者指出，面对海量且混乱的信息，真正的瓶颈并非阅读理解能力，而是缺乏决策前的信息整理和结构化思维。文章将原始文本比喻为一锅未过滤的汤，强调通过结构化方法过滤杂质的重要性。作者分享了一套实用的 AI Prompt，用于快速将混乱的文本信息拆解为客观事实、主观判断和需要回应的要点，从而高效剥离情绪、识别噪音，并明确沟通的核心。文章强调 AI 仅是辅助工具，最终的判断和决策仍需人类完成，并提出“不结构化，不决策”的核心理念，为读者提供了三条 actionable 的建议，以提升信息处理效率，避免沟通内耗。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "信息处理能力而非阅读理解，是拉开产品经理之间差距的关键。",
      "explanation": "面对杂乱无章的文本信息，真正的挑战在于缺乏将信息结构化、系统化整理的能力，而非单纯的文字理解障碍，强调有效信息整理对决策的重要性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "将混乱文本比喻为未过滤的汤，强调结构化是过滤信息杂质的关键步骤。",
      "explanation": "通过生动的比喻，指出大多数人在处理信息时，直接面对“带骨带油带浮沫”的原始信息，而高手则会先进行“过滤”和“提炼”，这就是结构化的核心价值。"
    },
    {
      "point": "分享了一套实用的 AI Prompt，辅助产品经理进行信息拆解与结构化。",
      "explanation": "该 Prompt 旨在将文本信息分解为核心概括、关键要点、区分事实/判断/情绪，并标注需要回应的决策点，极大地提高了信息处理效率，并将情绪与核心信息剥离。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 辅助工具的核心价值在于提升认知效率，而非替代决策。",
      "explanation": "明确指出 AI 负责结构化、标重点和识别情绪，但最终的立场、判断和决策仍需人类产品经理来完成，工具是辅助，而非终极解决方案。"
    },
    {
      "point": "提出了“不结构化，不决策”的理念和三条实践建议。",
